            Founded in 1938, Shufro, Rose & Company is registered with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission as a broker-dealer and investment adviser. It is a member of the New York Stock Exchange. Shufro, Rose & Company, also known as SRC, specializes in the discretionary management of investment portfolios. The company is independently owned by working members. Shufro, Rose & Company s clients maintain managed accounts in which it makes individualized investment decisions.
          






















